reviewText: Happy Halloween Amazon customers. This movie is great. My friends and I love the movie and always like to copy parts (like Skully having money in his "other pelvis"). Our favorite part was where Harry loses his signature shirt and even though they censor it you clearly see his body. I think Bert, Darrel, Katie, Hannah, and Jimmy have new voice actors. So I like both but this one much more. They both run for about an hour or so and the price is worth it.
